Description

Find your energy and feel your best with Fitbit Inspire 3 !

This little health hack on your wrist helps you stay on top of your stress, fitness and sleep--all you have to do is wear it. Track Health Metrics like skin temperature & blood oxygen, plus get daily scores that show how ready you are to workout or how well you're managing stress. Includes a 6-month Fitbit Premium membership. Fitbit is part of the Google family.

Features

  • This Exciting Bundle/Kit Includes: Fitbit Inspire 3 Health & Fitness Activity Tracker (Lilac Bliss / Black), Small & Large Bands, PremGear 3.3ft USB Charging Cable, PremGear Wall Adapter, 2 PremGear Screen Protectors & PremGear Quality Cleaning Cloth
  • DO WHAT YOU LOVE the best exercise is the one you love. Active Zone Minutes tracks your heart rate so you know when youre in fat burn, cardio peak zones and can adjust your effort to match your goals
  • JUST BREATHE IT OUT: Everyone feels stress how you respond to it makes the difference. Stress Management Score and guided breathing sessions can teach you healthier ways to handle it all
  • TIRED OF BEING TIRED? Better energy starts with better rest. Track your Sleep Score, light, deep & REM sleep, sleeping heart rate and how consistent your schedule is
  • KEEP AN EYE ON YOUR WELL-BEING: The Fitbit app is like a control panel for your body. By watching for changes in your resting heart rate, blood oxygen, skin temperature & more, you can get to know your body and do whats best for it
  • LIGHT AS AIR Thats how it feels to wear this slim, smooth silicone band FITBIT PREMIUM includes 6 months of Fitbit Premium so you can see your Daily Readiness Score and Sleep Profile. Plus try high-energy workouts from top fitness brands and mindfulness sessions for sleep, anxiety & more

      My FitBit is a Great Tool For My Daily Workouts
      Reviewed in the United States on October 25, 2024
      In the past, I always bought cheap fitness watches yet wanted to have a FitBit. I decided to splurge and I am glad I did. This watch has a much smaller face but has all the things I need, such as the step counter, sleep monitor, etc. I also like that it directly connects to... See more
      In the past, I always bought cheap fitness watches yet wanted to have a FitBit. I decided to splurge and I am glad I did. This watch has a much smaller face but has all the things I need, such as the step counter, sleep monitor, etc. I also like that it directly connects to the Weight Watcher's App. My doctor wanted me to get my health back in order so this is the perfect tool to help with that.

      Pros include:

      1. It holds battery charge pretty well. I charge it maybe every 5 days.
      2. I love the look. I bought a Tiger's Eye band and like that it doesn't have to look like a fitness watch with the giant screen.
      3. It tracks sleep and steps much better than cheaper smart watches. I have not had a problem with it skipping things. The last watch I had would work fine, then after sleeping for a good several hours, it wouldn't record anything at all. I need reliability and this watch seems to offer that.

      Cons:

      I'm not sure right now. Give me a few months and I might but I love the watch and believe that it was a great buy. As with all electronics, I am sure that over time, it will need to be replaced.
